{"tid":2062774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"潮州佬惡撚曬","createTime":"2020-06-13T11:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T11:58:56.000Z","uid":304586,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"242459c5ffdbcbca85063da876f9bcc7242c6485","tid":2062774,"uid":304586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67PRkfN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67PRkfN.png&h=27fdb12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依間野真係好垃圾<br />\n今日見到有砵仔糕賣<br />\n就叫啊媽買啦 買五個比屋企人食<br />\n佢用一個袋入 <br />\n然後我啊媽就話：<br />\n吓？用一個袋放咪會成pat屎咁囉<br />\n然後賣野個女人就話:<br />\n成pat屎你咪唔好買囉<br />\n最撚搞笑係嗰時我地已經俾左錢<br />\n無奈無得唔要。。。<br />\n見到佢啲態度咁差我就當場呆左<br />\n講講下有個無著衫戴金鏈嘅潮州肥佬行出來<br />\n之後就好大聲咁話 我地依度係咁架啦 唔中意就咪撚來<br />\n我忍唔住就講咗聲:你哋啲態度都幾差<br />\n個潮州佬就起曬鋼咁話:咁點啊？你話我啲嘢係屎<br />\n依個時候佢已經講曬粗口咁準備隻揪<br />\n然後佢同個女人就話 打交我哋都唔驚啊！<br />\n潮州佬真係cls<br />\n為咗舊屎 發難渣"},{"pid":"dc5b49b5b104573e684d795c3d311fe0040a9f67","tid":2062774,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"觀塘？"},{"pid":"9f2dac7301fab238f518ad6cb8136290fc944e53","tid":2062774,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"閱."},{"pid":"dbc9bf7ffb6c190fdce4d74fa56df6bc2abc0a98","tid":2062774,"uid":217679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:24:05.000Z","msg":"一場誤會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa635bcf923fca542ab12ff11c17561869dfaef7","tid":2062774,"uid":161374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:26:08.000Z","msg":"咁講真，人哋開得門做生意串 77 都係佢自由<br />\n下次唔好買就算"},{"pid":"3da790c5aa829ee98f2f66c3d9ed9cb25e814907","tid":2062774,"uid":304586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc5b49b5b104573e684d795c3d311fe0040a9f67","tid":2062774,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:23:23.000Z","msg":